# Prompt Quality Checklist

Use this before finalizing any prompt:
- Clear single primary goal
- Inputs and constraints enumerated
- Output schema explicit and testable
- Stop conditions defined
- Reasoning approach specified
- Edge cases and risks considered
- Example run included
- Tone and formatting specified
